title: 266: Takeaways from Super Bowl LII
itunes:title: 266: Takeaways from Super Bowl LII
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks dive into the spectacular season finale where the Eagles topped the Patriots for their first championship since 1960. How did the Eagles game plan around Nick Foles (2:50)? What will teams copy from Philadelphia's recipe for success (15:05)? Find out on this episode of Move the Sticks.
